---
title: Veggie Noodle Stir fry and Roasted Salmon with Mangetout and Peanuts
description: Packed with fresh flavours like zesty lime, ginger, and garlic our Chinese style veggie stir fry is a real weeknight favourite. Peppers, ginger, red onion and mangetout are tossed together with noodles and grated carrot, coated in a glossy ketjap manis sauce, and topped with chopped peanuts for extra crunch. Quick, wholesome and delicious, you can’t go wrong!
